Notes: The Golden Eagles spoil the Wildcats' Senior night, scoring 52 second half
points to beat Chico State at Acker Gym for the second straight season. The
loss drops the 'Cats back into a first place tie with UC San Diego in the CCAA
standings. Chico State wraps up the regular season on the road Wed. and Thurs.
Game.Officials: Chris,  Hirano,  Kim Mains,  David Arden
